Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we part.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Ouma Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I can't leave you... to your own devices...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Void? That entire town?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Roppongi Fort is a phantasm given form by a single girl's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Mana, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the Void information I promised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fare you paid only gets you this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cold man.
