Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:55.82,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\3c&HD46ACE&}I'll give that to you now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally show yourself... Daath grave keeper...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grave keeper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuichiro worked so hard that we decided to cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow him... Shu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They plan to... sacrifice Inori... to awaken Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you taking Inori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouma Shu, if you're that determined to come with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please do so after you've remembered everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the memories of Mana that you yourself sealed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu. All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your eyes now, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing, Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? This is your big sister's secret place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I'll tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shu. Ouma Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ouma Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're asking your name. Your {\i1}name{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Triton."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came from the sea. So you're Triton.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a great name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:06:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... My big sister Mana and I met a boy that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That boy Mana called "Triton"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And we spent a summer together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The year of Lost Christmas...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last summer we could all spend smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you serious about jumping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! Believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're next! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? You did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as we spent time together,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he became special to me enough to call him a best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:07:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had Mana, the gentle big sister I loved, and my best friend Gai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the happiest, most fun summer of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why... why did I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About Gai, and Mana too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awake now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this?! Please, give back Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl has never been more than an "instance body" we created
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to use as an interface for communication with Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words "give back" aren't really appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Created?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as the first person who ever touched the rock that started it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana was the first one infected with the Apocalypse Virus. In other words, Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her soul which had lost its body is now being poured into a new body,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thanks to our labors, she is about to set foot in this world again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her resurrection will mark the second coming of Lost Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Apocalypse Virus shall run rampant over all the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must bear witness to that event.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daath seems to have some hopes for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you ask me, you're just a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stand back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and watch quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's about to propose to Mana through Inori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Propose...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, her chosen partner
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will become the progenitor of the next generation, the new human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the selfish Eve can be controlled, if you use the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust we can count on you to bless their future together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. If I marry someone, will you be lonely, Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marry who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone! Maybe Triton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triton?! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joking, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never marry that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked at me with adult eyes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leering{\i0} eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think that's gross?{asuka feels sick}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}you{\i0} can look at me with adult eyes, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the virus, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those spots are from the virus in that rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad said it makes people go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do with Shu, Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who brought you back from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do whatever I want with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to tie the knot with Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't let anyone get in my way. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you'll marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{11:45 eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O ye chosen fittest pair, perform the coming together of blood
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that shall shape the new race.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shunned me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right there back then, wasn't I? Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember anything? Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to punish you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Shu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I can't leave you to your own devices!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai! What about your wounds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't hit any vital organs. The cancer crystals saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutsugami Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I can confront you... and Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hidden camera footage was as staticky this time as when I shot the Void,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I believe you can see it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sephirah's prototype filter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let us through?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was booted out of the arena, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my little way of picking on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.94,Destiny,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny can't be changed.{LET'S DESTINY}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi! Emergency bailout!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai, I can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral nuptial vows, here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some part of you must remember what happened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,December, 2029.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your new mother, Ouma Haruka, had brought us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on December 24th, I asked you to come to a church in Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you about the Mana you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the one who came...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my knight, aren't you Triton?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So keep on protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a shot at that star.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triton.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triton?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triton! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Triton?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use our genes to make a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do something fun together, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me... you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your big sister's scared, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate... I'll become someone who isn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so Mana ended up destroying herself with her own out-of-control power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Mana looked to us for help that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we couldn't give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Gai, you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was protecting myself by forgetting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu. You can tell right now, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have something we need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get Mana's heart back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They awakened her against her will,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're going to put her to sleep again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the Void's power to consign her bad will to oblivion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memory's shackles are undone, and you're in new king mode, eh, Ouma Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is running out. Draw out my heart, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then give me the Void!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you are right now, I know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw it out without letting go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is... Gai's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to cover me while I head for Mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling, Shu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Void that forces other Voids to manifest?!{hurrdurrplothax}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun that draws out people's hearts, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.23,0:19:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand down, Shuichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stab Mana right through me, Shu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dead man either way. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu, what do I look like to you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a child you were decisive, and brave, and... strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai! What are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can become me whenever you want. Just like I became you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the rest on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shu...{ED playing in background}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:45.82,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}What did you tell me when we parted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:52.46,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The words hung in midair and never reached me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:59.21,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I know my dreams and wishes are illusory
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.84,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}and yet I cannot give up on them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:15.85,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}You said, "Don't let go, hold onto my hand"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:22.86,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}and, "We will always be together"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:31.62,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Your hands as I held them were warm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:39.92,Copy of ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,2000)}and tender
