Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tri... ton?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana... I finally reached you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gai! {\i1}Gai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Gai is satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear him saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{end}
